name: Kestrel Development
body:
### Hello! Nice to meet you.
My name is Matthew Lewis, and I'm a computer engineering student at the University of Minnesota Twin Cities.

I'm using GitHub to share my code with other developers.

### Check me out!
My website can be found at [http://www.mplewis.com](mplewis.com), along with my [WordPress blog](http://www.mplewis.com/blog).

### Talk to me!
Feel free to email me at matt@mplewis.com if you have any questions.
tagline: All the code that's fit to compile.
